  <brief_title>E Test Strips Applied to Bronchoalveolar Lavage for Suspicion of Hospital-acquired Pneumonia to Accelerate Antibiogram Analysis.</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Université Victor Segalen Bordeaux 2</agency>
